NOW HIRING! $50 Sign-on bonus!<br>
Hit the road, deliver orders for Panera Bread, and earn up to $17 per hour with tips!<br>
<br>
Knowing our customers can't always get to a bakery-cafe to enjoy their Panera favorites, we're launching delivery service at our Western location.  This means we're looking for drivers to bring Panera Warmth -- along with our delicious food -- to them at their homes or places of business!<br>
<br>
A driver's primary responsibility is to coordinate the set-up and accuracy of orders, and then deliver them on-time with superior service!  Other duties may include secondary assignments in the cafe.<br>
<br>
APPLY TODAY to learn more:  work4panera.com and search for "driver" at your preferred location. EOE<br>
<br>
We Offer<br>
•	Mileage and tips PAID OUT DAILY<br>
•	FLEXIBLE work schedules to accommodate school, a 2nd job, or just life itself<br>
•	65% DISCOUNT on meals on a work day so you can enjoy our superior items, too<br>
•	$100 REFERRAL program for referring other drivers to Panera<br>
•	FUN and CASUAL work environment -- our uniform includes jeans!<br>
•	INSURANCE and matching 401(k) Plan (based on tenure and average hours worked)<br>
<br>
Requirements to Apply<br>
•	Ability to provide a warm and friendly customer experience<br>
•	Minimum age of 18 to drive<br>
•	Valid driver's license<br>
•	Current auto insurance and registration to a reliable vehicle to serve as your mobile office<br>
•	Motor Vehicle record in good standing<br>
•	Ability to pass background check<br>
<br>
Why Panera?<br>
•	Non-grease, tobacco-free environment <br>
•	No alcohol service or late-night deliveries<br>
•	Commitment to Clean Food (no preservatives or artificial ingredients)<br>
•	Community Focus (food banks and other charitable organizations)<br>
•	#1 ranking Chain Restaurant Best Reputation (Entrepreneur Magazine)<br>
•	World's Most Admired Companies (Fortune Magazine)<br>
    </section>

